Dinghy"},{"label":"Tube"},{"label":"SU Paddle Boards"},{"label":"Swim Platform\t"},{"label":"Fishing Gear"},{"label":"Wake Board"},{"label":"Water Skis Adult\t"},{"label":"Water Skis Kids"},{"label":"Sea Bobs\t"},{"label":"Kayaks 1 Pax"},{"label":"Snorkel Gear"}],"entertainment":["Salon TV","Salon Stereo","Onboard Wi-Fi"],"tenders":[]},"crew":[{"name":"Dimitris Christodoulou","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::d6d42980-90ba-11ef-a947-0f49700f3c90::assets::20ab3d90-4075-11f0-805c-2b9e65be814b/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"After my first experience with a sailing boat at the age of 14 I felt that my heart will always belong to the sea. At the age of 20 I joined the Greek Navy and after that I was a member of the Hellenic Coast Guard for 17 years. For the last 5 years I am working as a skipper, mostly with sailing boats. I am Greek, Non Smoker, I love cooking, exploring and learning about new countries and cultures I have got Offshore sailing diploma, Motor boat diploma up to 100kor, Cosmos Nautical Academy courses for firefighting-survival first aid and crisis management."},{"name":"Victoria Makovska","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::d6d42980-90ba-11ef-a947-0f49700f3c90::assets::3cae69e0-4075-11f0-805c-2b9e65be814b/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Victoria was born in Ukraine and raised between Ukraine Germany and Russia. She has been living in Greece for the past 23 years. She has 20 years of working experience in customer service making sure everybody meets their requests. Always smiling, filling up the place with her positive energy and calmness."},{"name":"Loukianos Gagos","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::d6d42980-90ba-11ef-a947-0f49700f3c90::assets::48976cc0-4075-11f0-805c-2b9e65be814b/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Loukianos is a passionate fresh sea man, who is looking for adventure. Always positive and willing to do the best for the crew and the guests.\nTravelled from France (Les Sables-d'Olonne) to Greece on a catamaran, and worked on a traditional wooden boat in Mykonos. Also has a few years experience as a watersports instructor (surfing, kitesurfing, sup) and sea kayak tour guide. He wants to share with people the joy of the water element. His dream is to visit many places and make friends all around the world."}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"EUR","price":3000000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":3000000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"EUR","price":4100000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":4100000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"High Season (July/August)","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2025-07-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2025-08-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2026-07-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-08-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2027-07-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2027-08-31T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"currency":"EUR","charterFee":4100000,"inputAmountTaxed":"EXCLUSIVE","note":"","unit":"WEEK","lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","quantity":1,"unitPrice":4100000,"amount":4100000,"conditions":"Weekly","taxRate":{"label":"VAT","value":0.12}},{"item":"APA","conditions":"","quantity":0.2,"unitPrice":4100000,"amount":820000}],"total":5412000,"subTotal":4920000,"totalTax":492000},"inclusionZones":[{"label":"Greece","type":"Sovereign country","category":["Europe","Southern Europe","Greece"],"coordinates":[24.261736188816826,38.42232351533858],"bbox":[19.646484375,34.934472656249994,28.231835937500023,41.743798828124994]}],"exclusionZones":[],"petsAllowed":false},{"name":"Mid Season (June/September)","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2025-06-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2025-06-30T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2026-06-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-06-30T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2027-06-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2027-06-30T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2025-09-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2025-09-30T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2026-09-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-09-30T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2027-09-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2027-09-30T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"currency":"EUR","char